{
  "1": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Yahweh gave to Jeremiah the prophet a message about Babylon and the country of Babylonia.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "p",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "paragraph"
      }
    ]
  },
  "2": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "This is what Yahweh says:\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "\"Proclaim a message among the nations;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "do not withhold any of it;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "raise up a signal flag\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "to announce that Babylon will be captured.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Its chief god Marduk, whose other name is Bel, will be completely disgraced,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and all the other statues and idols will be shattered.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "3": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "The army of a nation will come from the north to attack Babylon\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and destroy the city very thoroughly,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "with the result that no one will live there again.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Both people and animals will run away.\"\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "4": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\"But I, Yahweh, say that in the future, when that is about to happen,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "the people of Israel and the people of Judah will join together.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "They will be weeping\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and wanting to worship me, their God.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "5": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "They will inquire about the road to Jerusalem,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and then they will start traveling toward it.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "They will say to each other,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "'We must return to Yahweh again!'\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "They will make an everlasting agreement with me that they will never forget.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "6": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "My people have been like lost sheep.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Their leaders have caused them to abandon me\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "like shepherds who have allowed their sheep to wander in the hills and mountains.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "My people are like sheep\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "that do not know the path to return to the sheepfold.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "7": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "All their enemies who found them attacked them.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "They said, 'We did not sin by attacking them,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "because they sinned against Yahweh;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "he is the one who provides what they need;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "he is the one to whom they should have remained faithful;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "he is the one whom their ancestors confidently expected to help them.'\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "8": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "But now, I say to the leaders of my people, 'Depart from Babylon!\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Leave the land of Babylonia!\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Act like male goats that go in front of the rest of the flock;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "lead my people back to their own land.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "9": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Do that because I am going to gather an army of great nations to the north of Babylon.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "They will join together to attack Babylon and will capture it.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Their arrows will be like skilled warriors\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "that always hit what they are aiming at.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "10": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Babylonia will be conquered,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and those who conquer it will take away everything they want.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "That will surely happen because I, Yahweh, have said it.'\"\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "11": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\"You people of Babylon who plundered my chosen people,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "now you are very happy.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "You run around joyfully like a calf in a meadow,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and are happy like stallions are happy when they are neighing.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "12": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "But soon your people will be very disgraced as a result of being conquered.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Your country will be the most insignificant nation;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "it will be a wilderness, a dry land and a desert plain.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "13": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Because I, Yahweh, am angry with you people of Babylon,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "I will cause your city to become completely deserted.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "All who pass by will be horrified\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and will gasp because of the destruction there.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "14": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "All you nations that surround Babylon,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "prepare to attack it!\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Tell your archers to shoot at their enemies;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "shoot all of your arrows at them and do not hold back,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "because the people of Babylon have sinned against me, Yahweh.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "15": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Shout victorious war cries against Babylon from all sides of the city.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "The soldiers of Babylon will surrender;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "the towers and walls will be torn down.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "It is I, Yahweh, who will be getting revenge on the people of Babylon,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and I will use you to get revenge.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Do to the people of Babylon what they have done to others!\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "16": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Take away from Babylon those who plant crops\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and those who reap the harvests!\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Because of the swords carried by those who will attack Babylon,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "the people in Babylon who have come from other countries\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "should all run away; they should go back to their own countries.\"\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "17": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\"The Israelite people are like sheep\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "that have been scattered by lions.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "First the army of the king of Assyria defeated them.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Then the army of King Nebuchadnezzar of Babylon smashed them.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "p",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "paragraph"
      }
    ]
  },
  "18": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "So this is what I, Yahweh, commander of the angel armies, the God whom Israel worships, say:\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "'Now I will punish the king of Babylon and the people of his land,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "like I punished the king of Assyria.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "19": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "And I will bring the people of Israel back to their own land\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "where they will eat the food that grows in the fields of the regions of Carmel and Bashan,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and the people in the hill areas of Ephraim and Gilead will have all they want to eat.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "20": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "At that time, there will not be people in Israel and in Judah who are still guilty for having sinned ,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "because I will forgive the small group of people whom I enable to still be alive.'\"\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "21": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\"So, I, Yahweh, say to the enemies of Babylonia, 'Attack the people who live in the region of Merathaim\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and the people in the region of Pekod of Babylonia.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Pursue them to kill them, and completely get rid of every single one of them,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "as I have commanded you to do.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "22": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Shout your battle cries throughout the land;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "shout when you are causing great destruction.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "23": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "The army of Babylon is like the most powerful hammer on the earth,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "but it will be completely shattered.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Babylon, one of the nations, will be a complete ruin.'\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "24": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "You people of Babylon, listen,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "because I have set a trap for you without your awareness;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "you will be caught in that trap,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "because you fought against me.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "25": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "It is as though I have opened the place where I store my weapons,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and I have brought out all the weapons\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "to use against the people with whom I am angry.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "I, Yahweh, commander of the angel armies, have a lot of work to do\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "to punish the people of Babylonia.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "26": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "So, you enemies of Babylonia, come from distant lands and attack it.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Break open the places where they store the grain,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and pile up the rubble like heaps of grain.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Destroy everything completely;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "do not leave anything that is not destroyed.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "27": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Destroy all the young warriors who are as strong as bulls;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "take them to where you will slaughter them.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "It will be terrible for them,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "because it will be time for them to be punished.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "28": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Listen to the people who have fled and escaped from Babylon\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "while they tell in Jerusalem how I, Yahweh, have gotten revenge against those who destroyed my temple in Jerusalem.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "29": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Summon archers to come to attack Babylon;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "surround the city\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "in order that no one will escape.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Do to the people of Babylon what they have done to others ,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "because they have defied me, the Holy One of the Israelite people.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "30": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "The young men of Babylon will fall in the streets;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "all their soldiers will be killed in one day. This will happen because I, Yahweh, have declared it!\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "31": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "I, Yahweh, commander of the angel armies, say this:\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "'You arrogant people,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "it is now the time;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "it is the day when I will punish you.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "32": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Your land is full of proud people,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "but you will stumble and fall,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and no one will lift you up again.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "I will light a fire in the cities of Babylonia\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "that will burn up everything that is nearby.'\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "p",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "paragraph"
      }
    ]
  },
  "33": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "I, Yahweh, commander of the angel armies, also say this:\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "'The people of Israel and Judah were oppressed;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "those who captured them guarded them carefully and would not allow them to leave Babylon.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "34": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "But Yahweh is strong, and he will free them.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Yahweh is the Commander of the angel armies;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "He will defend his people\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and enable them to return to their land where they will have peace,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "but the people of Babylonia will not have peace.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "35": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "He will send enemy soldiers carrying swords to strike the people of Babylonia;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "they will strike the officials and wise men\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and all the other people who live in Babylon.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "36": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "They will strike their false prophets with swords\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and they will become foolish.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "They will strike the strongest warriors of Babylonia,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and they will all be terrified.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "37": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "They will strike their horses and chariots\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and the foreign mercenaries who are in the army of Babylonia,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and they will all become as weak as women.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "They will seize all the valuable things there in Babylon\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and take them away.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "38": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Yahweh will cause the streams to become dry.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "He will do all those things because the entire land of Babylonia is filled with idols,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and those horrible idols have caused the people who worship them to become crazy.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "39": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Soon only jackals and other wild creatures will live there;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and it will be a place where ostriches live.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "People will never live there again;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "it will be uninhabited forever .\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "40": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Yahweh God will destroy Babylon like he destroyed Sodom and Gomorrah and the nearby towns;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "no one will ever live there again.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "41": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Look! A great army will come from the north.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "A great nation far away with many kings is preparing to attack you people of Babylon.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "42": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Their army has bows and arrows and spears;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "they are very cruel, and do not act mercifully to anyone.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "As they ride along on their horses,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "the sound of the horses' hooves is like the roaring of the ocean waves;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "they are riding in battle formation\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "to attack you, you people of Babylon.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "43": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "The king of Babylon heard their report,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "\"The enemy is approaching.\"\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "So he was frightened and became weak.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "Fear and anguish gripped him,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "like a woman who is about to give birth to a baby.\"\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "44": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "I, Yahweh, will come to Babylon suddenly like a lion comes out of the jungle\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and leaps on the sheep that are eating the good pastureland.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "I will quickly chase the people of Babylonia from their land.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "And then I will appoint for them a leader whom I will choose;\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "I will do that because there is no one like me who can say that what I have done is not right.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "No ruler can oppose me.\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "45": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Listen to what I have planned to do to the people of Babylon city and the rest of Babylonia:\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "even the little children will be dragged away,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and I will completely destroy the people who live there.\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "quote"
      }
    ]
  },
  "46": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "When Babylon is destroyed, the noise will be extremely loud,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q2",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "with the result that the earth will shake,\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "q1",
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "and the wailing of the people will be heard by the people of other nations.'\"\n"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n\n"
      },
      {
        "tag": "s5",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "section"
      }
    ]
  },
  "front": {
    "verseObjects": [
      {
        "tag": "p",
        "nextChar": "\n",
        "type": "paragraph"
      }
    ]
  }
}